tregon qarte se Ai ishte misherimi i  Shri Ganesh.

22
00:16:19,781 --> 00:16:23,115
Eshte nje prove shkencore qe ne kemi tani,

23
00:16:23,490 --> 00:16:29,115
dhe keshtu mund t'u themi njerezve qe eshte nje fakt.

24
00:16:30,574 --> 00:16:34,073
Une nuk e di ne kohen e Krishtit

25
00:16:34,449 --> 00:16:38,240
nese kjo alfa dhe omega ishin te njohura per matematikanet,

26
00:16:38,614 --> 00:16:40,865
por  patjeter per Ate

27
00:16:41,282 --> 00:16:45,990
kur Ai tha,"Une jam Alfa dhe Omega,"

28
00:16:53,740 --> 00:16:59,032
Ai ishte nje misherim shume i mrekullueshem,

29
00:16:59,615 --> 00:17:04,740
dhe shume i rendesishem per ngritjen tone.

30
00:17:06,282 --> 00:17:09,656
Nese Ai nuk do te kishte ringjallur Veten,

31
00:17:10,073 --> 00:17:14,198
ne s'mund te kishim arritur aspak ngritjen tone.

32
00:17:14,823 --> 00:17:17,615
Pra eshte nje kontribut i madh.

33
00:17:18,115 --> 00:17:22,865
Ringjallja e Krishtit eshte evidente tani ne jeten tone:

34
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:26,823
cfare ishit me pare

35
00:17:27,198 --> 00:17:30,407
dhe cfare jeni ju sot.

36
00:17:33,365 --> 00:17:36,324
Eshte nje ndryshim i tille,

37
00:17:36,740 --> 00:17:38,865
nje diference e tille,

38
00:17:39,157 --> 00:17:42,115
nje transformim i tille.

39
00:17:42,990 --> 00:17:46,574
Eshte sakrifica e Tij

40
00:17:47,032 --> 00:17:48,490
ne kryq

41
00:17:48,740 --> 00:17:52,490
dhe ringjallja e bukur

42
00:17:52,948 --> 00:17:55,532
e Tij

43
00:17:55,823 --> 00:17:59,032
ka krijuar nje menyre per te gjithe ne

44
00:17:59,365 --> 00:18:04,614
per t'u futur ne nje gjendje te re transformimi.

45
00:18:09,324 --> 00:18:15,240
Ne kete gjendje eshte nje histori e ndryshme per qeniet njerezore,

46
00:18:15,614 --> 00:18:18,073
dhe e ndryshme per Krishtin.

47
00:18:18,407 --> 00:18:20,490
Krishti ishte Vetja e tij

48
00:18:20,823 --> 00:18:24,990
ishte shenjteria, ishte pastertia.

49
00:18:26,449 --> 00:18:28,948
Pra ringjallja e Tij

50
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:35,698
s'eshte asgje por nje ngjarje fizike, mund te themi,

51
00:18:37,324 --> 00:18:41,198
sepse Ai s'kishte nevoje per transformimin,

52
00:18:42,823 --> 00:18:44,781
Ai nuk kishte

53
00:18:45,073 --> 00:18:49,574
pse te kalonte nepermjet ndonje pastrimi.

54
00:18:51,032 --> 00:18:54,365
Por ajo qe ndodhi ne rastin e Tij

55
00:18:55,032 --> 00:19:00,157
ishte qe Ai u

56
00:19:01,614 --> 00:19:04,823
ringjall nga vdekja

57
00:19:05,324 --> 00:19:09,865
"simbolizon jeten e qenieve njerezore pa spiritualitet"

58
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:12,823
eshte si vdekja;

59
00:19:13,198 --> 00:19:15,198
sepse ata bejne gjithcka

60
00:19:15,574 --> 00:19:21,157
pa kuptuar asgje ne lidhje me teresine,

61
00:19:22,365 --> 00:19:24,532
ne lidhje me realitetin,

62
00:19:24,865 --> 00:19:27,906
me te verteten absolute.

63
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:30,490
Se fundi cfaredo qe ata te bejne

64
00:19:30,906 --> 00:19:34,990
i con drejt shkaterrimit te tyre.

65
00:19:36,656 --> 00:19:39,990
Madje edhe fete qe jane krijuar

66
00:19:40,365 --> 00:19:42,449
prej ketyre misherimeve te medha

67
00:19:42,823 --> 00:19:47,240
jane ne renie (degradim) absolute.

68
00:19:47,615 --> 00:19:51,615
Nuk do te gjeni asnje gjurme te jetes religjioze

69
00:19:52,032 --> 00:19:53,532
tek te gjithe ata njerez

70
00:19:53,865 --> 00:19:56,740
te cilet pretendojne se jane ata

71
00:19:57,073 --> 00:20:00,865
qe mund t'i shfaqin (manifestojne) keto misherime.

72
00:20:01,574 --> 00:20:04,615
Nese e shihni ne nje menyre me te thelle

73
00:20:05,032 --> 00:20:06,948
eshte edhe shume e dhimbshme.

74
00:20:07,324 --> 00:20:11,449
qe ne emer te gjithe ketyre misherimeve te medha

75
00:20:11,823 --> 00:20:14,365
gjerat qe njerezit po bejne,

76
00:20:14,781 --> 00:20:19,324
aktivitetet qe ata ndermarrin eshte dicka e pamundur,

77
00:20:19,656 --> 00:20:22,614
sepse nuk kane frike nga Zoti.

78
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:26,115
Ne emer te Zotit jane duke bere gjithe keto gjera te tmerrshme

79
00:20:26,407 --> 00:20:28,115
ne mbare boten.

80
00:20:28,449 --> 00:20:29,532
Sigurisht qe ketu,

81
00:20:29,823 --> 00:20:31,740
mund te thoni qe Kisha Katolike ka qene ekspozuar.

82
00:20:32,073 --> 00:20:33,990
Gjithkund njerezit po shohin

83
00:20:34,407 --> 00:20:37,656
qe jane ekspozuar gjithe keto gjera fallse .

84
00:20:38,032 --> 00:20:41,906
Por gjithe keto gjera false ata i kane perdorur

85
00:20:42,449 --> 00:20:46,365
nen petkun e Zotit,

86
00:20:46,656 --> 00:20:49,574
spiritualizmit dhe bukurise.

87
00:20:49,990 --> 00:20:53,198
Kjo eshte menyra me e mire per ta fshehur.

88
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:58,698
Gjithe mizoria, gjithe dhuna,

89
00:20:59,615 --> 00:21:02,532
gjithe shemtia

90
00:21:03,449 --> 00:21:05,865
"keshtu kane funksionuar ata."

91
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:09,948
Dhe ka shkuar ne nje gjendje te tille

92
00:21:10,365 --> 00:21:13,365
sa ju nuk mund te gjeni as edhe nje nuance.

93
00:21:13,781 --> 00:21:18,240
te vogel te jetes fetare ne mesin e ketyre njerezve.

94
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:20,656
Si te gjithe hajdutet e botes,

95
00:21:20,990 --> 00:21:22,948
gjithe kriminelet e botes

96
00:21:23,365 --> 00:21:26,948
dhe gjithe intriguesit e botes ta kene marre persiper.

97
00:21:29,198 --> 00:21:33,490
Kjo ndodh sepse ajo qe eshte shkruar ne te gjithe librat

98
00:21:33,823 --> 00:21:37,656
dhe te gjithe shkrimet e shenjta qe keni kerkuar per veten,

99
00:21:38,157 --> 00:21:40,615
nuk jane bere kurre.

100
00:21:42,157 --> 00:21:45,614
"Te duhet te njohesh veten" nuk eshte bere kurre.

101
00:21:45,990 --> 00:21:49,449
Sa here ka thene Krishti, "Njih vetveten."

102
00:21:49,865 --> 00:21:52,240
Ai gjithashtu tha "Ju do te lindni perseri"

103
00:21:52,656 --> 00:21:55,532
"keshtu menjehere ata moren nje certifikate, "Une linda perseri"

104
00:21:55,906 --> 00:22:01,365
dhe filluan te perfitonin me kete lloj certifikate.

105
00:22:02,948 --> 00:22:05,656
Por faktikisht ata nuk mendojne

106
00:22:06,032 --> 00:22:08,615
cfare mireqenie iu eshte dhene.

107
00:22:09,032 --> 00:22:10,865
Me e shumta ata mund te kene bere ca para,

108
00:22:11,282 --> 00:22:14,656
me e shumta ata mund te kene patur disa fuqi siperfaqesore;

109
00:22:15,032 --> 00:22:21,032
por s'eshte bere asgje, nese e shikon nga natyra e lindur.

110
00:22:23,532 --> 00:22:27,781
Mund te misherosh cmendurine e tyre,

111
00:22:28,532 --> 00:22:32,240
per menyren si e kane marre jeten e Krishtit

112
00:22:32,614 --> 00:22:34,157
apo jeten e ndonje tjetri

113
00:22:34,532 --> 00:22:38,865
shume fisnik dhe me nje sistem me te larte vlerash,

114
00:22:39,324 --> 00:22:45,365
dhe po bejne gjera te nje shkalle shume te ulet.

115
00:22:47,324 --> 00:22:52,532
Tani ne Sahaja Yoga ju keni transformuar veten tuaj.

116
00:22:53,115 --> 00:22:56,698
Do te thoja qe kundalini juaj e ka bere punen.

117
00:22:57,365 --> 00:23:01,407
Por ende diferenca mes Krishtit dhe jush eshte kjo,

118
00:23:01,781 --> 00:23:06,407
qe ju po vini nga ai ambjent,

119
00:23:07,490 --> 00:23:09,614
nga ai stil jete,

120
00:23:09,990 --> 00:23:12,240
nga ajo menyre e te menduarit

121
00:23:12,614 --> 00:23:14,823
qe ishte per te gjithe shkaterrimin tuaj.

122
00:23:15,198 --> 00:23:19,490
Nese shikoni gjithcka tani eshte per shkaterrimin tuaj.

123
00:23:19,990 --> 00:23:22,532
Prandaj kur ju dilni prej saj,

124
00:23:22,990 --> 00:23:25,990
perseri keto gjera te bejne me dhimbje koke (dehin),

125
00:23:26,407 --> 00:23:31,365
perseri ju ndikoheni prej tyre.

126
00:23:31,906 --> 00:23:34,574
Edhe kur ju po ngriheni lart e me lart,

127
00:23:34,865 --> 00:23:38,157
ju duket papritur sikur po terhiqeni poshte perseri

128
00:23:38,490 --> 00:23:41,032
ne disa lloj situatash qesharake,

129
00:23:41,365 --> 00:23:46,823
ne disa lloj gjerash degraduese.

130
00:23:47,449 --> 00:23:50,282
Sigurisht, ndonjehere tronditeni me veten tuaj;

131
00:23:50,656 --> 00:23:53,532
ndonjehere e pranoni gjithe kete.

132
00:23:53,990 --> 00:23:56,324
Pra per nje Sahaja yogi eshte shume e rendesishme

133
00:23:56,614 --> 00:23:58,407
qe pasi ka ardhur tek realizimi

134
00:23:58,823 --> 00:24:01,823
duhet te behet shume introspektiv (te shohe brenda vetes).

135
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:04,073
Ne vend te qe te shohe gjerat e keqija te tjereve,

136
00:24:04,407 --> 00:24:08,198
ai duhet te provoje te shohe c'eshte e keqe brenda vetes se tij.

137
00:24:08,740 --> 00:24:12,948
Eshte shume e rendesishme qe ju duhet te dini se

138
00:24:13,365 --> 00:24:17,282
sa larg po shkoni drejt spiritualizmit tuaj.

139
00:24:17,948 --> 00:24:22,157
Sepse Krishti nuk kishte nevoje per kete,

140
00:24:22,781 --> 00:24:26,490
Ai madje nuk kishte pse te bente introspektive per Veten e Tij.

141
00:24:26,990 --> 00:24:33,324
Ai ishte dicka qe ishte pertej cdokorrupsioni,

142
00:24:34,198 --> 00:24:40,490
dhe per Te ishte thjesht nje transformim fizik,

143
00:24:40,823 --> 00:24:43,157
ne kuptimin qe, meqe Ai vdiq

144
00:24:43,614 --> 00:24:46,656
atehere Ai ringjalli Veten.

145
00:24:47,115 --> 00:24:50,365
Por per ne eshte shume ndryshe.

146
00:24:50,781 --> 00:24:53,781
Ne tani jemi Sahaja yogis,

147
00:24:54,157 --> 00:24:57,656
por ne jemi qenie te zakonshme njerezore.

148
00:24:58,073 --> 00:25:00,532
Ne s'kemi drite brenda nesh.

149
00:25:00,906 --> 00:25:02,948
Tani drita vjen brenda nesh

150
00:25:03,324 --> 00:25:05,614
dhe ne shohim driten,

151
00:25:05,948 --> 00:25:09,324
me pas cfare behemi?

152
00:25:09,698 --> 00:25:13,198
Ne duhet te behemi vete drita.

153
00:25:13,740 --> 00:25:15,365
Krishti ishte drita.

154
00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:17,282
Ai nuk duhej te behej.

155
00:25:17,615 --> 00:25:19,615
Pra ne duhet te behemi drita.

156
00:25:19,906 --> 00:25:23,823
Dhe tani ju duhet te ruani

157
00:25:24,698 --> 00:25:28,282
menyren qe kjo drite mund te trazohet,

158
00:25:28,615 --> 00:25:33,948
mund te reduktohet, ose mund te shuhet plotesisht.

159
00:25:35,615 --> 00:25:40,073
Pra mbajeni veten me kete drite,

160
00:25:40,407 --> 00:25:42,781
gjeja e pare ju duhet te dini qe

161
00:25:43,198 --> 00:25:45,449
nese ju shihni driten, nuk eshte e duhura

162
00:25:45,781 --> 00:25:47,115
"do te thote qe ju s'jeni drita.

163
00:25:47,490 --> 00:25:50,948
Ju duhet te beheni drita.

164
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:53,781
Kur ju jeni drita,

165
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:56,823
atehere ne kete drite ju mund te shihni lehtesisht

166
00:25:57,157 --> 00:25:59,656
si punon mendja juaj,

167
00:26:00,157 --> 00:26:02,240
cfare idesh ju jep,

168
00:26:02,615 --> 00:26:09,157
cfare ndikon tek mendja juaj

169
00:26:09,865 --> 00:26:11,823
ndersa ju po ngriheni.

170
00:26:12,157 --> 00:26:14,073
Eshte ky shqetesimi

171
00:26:14,365 --> 00:26:19,865
apo eshte kjo pergjegjesia qe keni?

172
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:24,490
Ose eshte kjo prej zakoneve te keqija qe keni patur,

173
00:26:24,906 --> 00:26:26,656
qe ka nje pengese

174
00:26:27,032 --> 00:26:32,157
ne rritjen tuaj si nje personalitet shpirteror?

175
00:26:32,865 --> 00:26:35,614
Pra ju duhet te ruani veten gjate gjithe kohes,

176
00:26:35,990 --> 00:26:40,990
dhe te shihni veten se si po procedoni.

177
00:26:42,490 --> 00:26:45,490
Eshte nje udhetim shume i bukur

178
00:26:45,865 --> 00:26:47,574
"udhetim shume shume i bukur.

179
00:26:48,032 --> 00:26:50,240
Dje isha shume e lumtur te degjoja

180
00:26:50,614 --> 00:26:55,240
kengen e Ruseve qe pershkruanin udhetimin,

181
00:26:56,407 --> 00:27:01,490
udhetim i kundalinit.

182
00:27:03,574 --> 00:27:11,198
Kjo eshte e vertete, pa dyshim, qe ju jeni shpirtra te realizuar.

183
00:27:12,865 --> 00:27:17,574
Parimisht ju nuk ishit nje shpirt i realizuar,

184
00:27:18,157 --> 00:27:20,823
por tani ju jeni nje shpirt i realizuar.

185
00:27:21,324 --> 00:27:23,198
Ju jeni nje gjendje e zhvilluar.

186
00:27:23,656 --> 00:27:29,407
Tani ajo cfare mungon eshte idea

187
00:27:29,865 --> 00:27:34,823
qe ne jemi plotesisht mire

188
00:27:35,324 --> 00:27:39,615
dhe asgje s'mund te na demtoje, te na perule.

189
00:27:41,032 --> 00:27:45,656
Nese ju zhvilloni nje ide te tille egoistike,

190
00:27:46,157 --> 00:27:48,823
nuk ka per t'ju ndihmuar aspak.

191
00:27:49,324 --> 00:27:52,324
Ajo qe ju duhet te beni eshte te

192
00:27:53,115 --> 00:27:54,948
beni introspektive ndaj vetes gjithe kohes.

193
00:27:55,365 --> 00:27:57,532
Per kete eshte meditimi,

194
00:27:57,906 --> 00:27:59,449
te shihni per veten

195
00:27:59,781 --> 00:28:03,906
si po e mbani lart

196
00:28:04,407 --> 00:28:07,574
ngritjen tuaj shpirterore.

197
00:28:08,073 --> 00:28:09,490
Askush tjeter s'mund ta beje,

198
00:28:09,906 --> 00:28:12,324
eshte puna juaj individuale.

199
00:28:12,614 --> 00:28:14,574
Sigurisht, nese shkoni ne kolektivitet, menjehere

200
00:28:14,823 --> 00:28:17,615
ata do te dine cilat cakra kane ngerce, pa asnje dyshim.

201
00:28:17,990 --> 00:28:21,740
Ata mund te mos e thone, ata mund te mos i referohen,

202
00:28:22,157 --> 00:28:23,614
por patjeter qe do te dijne

203
00:28:23,990 --> 00:28:25,740
qe kjo e ajo cakra eshte infektuar

204
00:28:26,157 --> 00:28:28,073
dhe ky person ka kete problem.

205
00:28:28,490 --> 00:28:33,198
Por ata nuk do te dijne per veten e tyre cilat cakra kane ngerce,

206
00:28:34,740 --> 00:28:37,698
cili eshte problemi i tyre.

207
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:40,157
Keshtu nese dikush ju thote

208
00:28:40,532 --> 00:28:42,407
qe "Mendoj se kjo cakra ka ngerce tek ty,"

209
00:28:42,698 --> 00:28:45,407
ju kurre, kurre nuk duhet te ndiheni keq per kete,

210
00:28:45,740 --> 00:28:48,449
sepse duke e mbajtur kete cakra te paprekur (patrajtuar)

211
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:51,656
ju jeni duke rrenuar jeten tuaj.

212
00:28:52,157 --> 00:28:54,614
Pra ajo cfare duhet te beni eshte te shihni

213
00:28:54,990 --> 00:28:56,740
qe nese dikush ju thote juve qe

214
00:28:57,115 --> 00:29:01,032
"Une mendoj qe eshte kjo cakra, ka dicka qe nuk shkon,"

215
00:29:01,407 --> 00:29:03,990
ju duhet ta falenderoni kete person, "Fale Zotit, qe me treguat."

216
00:29:04,407 --> 00:29:06,990
Si pasqyra "nese shiheni ne pasqyre

217
00:29:07,365 --> 00:29:09,532
dhe ka dicka qe s'shkon ne fytyren tuaj,

218
00:29:09,823 --> 00:29:11,240
ju mund ta korrigjoni ate menjehere.

219
00:29:11,614 --> 00:29:15,240
Ne te njejten menyre nese dikush konstaton kete tek ju,

220
00:29:15,615 --> 00:29:19,032
duhet te jesh mjaft i matur qe te dish

221
00:29:19,365 --> 00:29:21,032
se ky eshte nje bekim i madh

222
00:29:21,449 --> 00:29:24,532
qe nje gje e tille eshte nxjerre (konstatuar) tek ty.

223
00:29:25,532 --> 00:29:27,198
Si dje qe kishte nje grindje

224
00:29:27,532 --> 00:29:28,948
midis dy liderve.

225
00:29:29,324 --> 00:29:31,781
Gjithmone "ku ka dy lidere, gjithmone ka grindje.

226
00:29:32,073 --> 00:29:33,365
Nuk duhet te kete.

227
00:29:33,574 --> 00:29:37,157
Eshte tamam si dy sy qe nuk ndeshen kurre, dy duar s'ndeshen kurre,

228
00:29:37,532 --> 00:29:38,823
dy kembe nuk ndeshen.

229
00:29:39,198 --> 00:29:42,115
Por nese ka dy lidere, ka gjithmone nje problem.

230
00:29:42,532 --> 00:29:46,656
Duhet te keni gjithmone nje lider, perndryshe problem i madh.

231
00:29:47,449 --> 00:29:50,240
Keshtu ata po debatonin mes vetes, shikoni,

232
00:29:50,614 --> 00:29:55,198
dy lidere qe po debatonin mes tyre, dhe erdhen tek Une.

233
00:29:55,698 --> 00:29:59,240
E pashe menjehere qe njeri prej tyre ishte i prekur.

234
00:29:59,698 --> 00:30:01,906
I thashe, "Veri duart kundrejt Meje."

235
00:30:02,324 --> 00:30:03,906
Kur e vuri doren drejt Meje,

236
00:30:04,324 --> 00:30:07,198
e terhoqi menjehere mbrapsht. "Cfare ndodhi?"

237
00:30:07,532 --> 00:30:09,740
Ai tha, "Kam nje ndjesi djegie, Nene."

238
00:30:10,115 --> 00:30:13,948
I them, "Kjo eshte. Tani do te dish cili eshte problemi me ty?"

239
00:30:14,324 --> 00:30:16,449
Ai tha, "Une jam gjaknxehte, kete e di.

240
00:30:16,781 --> 00:30:20,490
Une jam shume egoistik. Nuk duhej te isha sjelle keshtu."

241
00:30:21,324 --> 00:30:26,574
Por ne te njejten kohe ai mund te jete ndjere shume keq,

242
00:30:26,948 --> 00:30:29,490
per shkak se ia thashe.

243
00:30:30,115 --> 00:30:33,073
Por ai nuk u ndje sepse eshte nje Sahaja yogi

244
00:30:33,574 --> 00:30:35,407
dhe ai e di cila eshte e mira per te,

245
00:30:35,823 --> 00:30:36,865
cfare eshte mire per te.

246
00:30:37,157 --> 00:30:38,615
Ai nuk u ndje aspak keq.

247
00:30:38,990 --> 00:30:41,115
Perkundrazi, ai ishte kaq mirenjohes ndaj Meje

248
00:30:41,490 --> 00:30:44,282
"Nene, fale teje une munda ta kuptoja.

249
00:30:44,656 --> 00:30:49,032
Perndryshe une po e fshihja brenda zemres sime."

250
00:30:56,032 --> 00:30:59,615
Tani, problemi me ne eshte qe

251
00:30:59,948 --> 00:31:04,240
ne kemi arritur mjaft zhvillim brenda vetes,

252
00:31:05,324 --> 00:31:07,740
dhe ne e kemi konsoliduar ate.

253
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:10,240
Gjithashtu, ne kemi nje fuqi te madhe kolektive,

254
00:31:10,615 --> 00:31:13,115
Mund ta shoh, ne cdo vend.

255
00:31:13,574 --> 00:31:16,282
Ne mund tu japim realizim shume veteve,

256
00:31:16,740 --> 00:31:19,282
dhe ne vertet mund  te formojme

257
00:31:19,698 --> 00:31:24,407
gjithe keto te verteta ne jetet tona.

258
00:31:24,823 --> 00:31:26,240
Ne mund ta bejme kete.

259
00:31:26,574 --> 00:31:30,115
Gjithe kohes ne duhet t'i stabilizojme ato.

260
00:31:30,906 --> 00:31:34,282
Por ka nje pike

261
00:31:34,656 --> 00:31:37,740
ne te cilen njeriu duhet te jete shume i sigurte:

262
00:31:38,198 --> 00:31:44,365
qe ju keni arritur absolutisht te verteten e fundit.

263
00:31:45,365 --> 00:31:48,032
Duhet te jeni shume te kujdesshem ne kete pike, shume.

264
00:31:48,449 --> 00:31:54,240
Kam pare njerez qe shkojne shume lart ne Sahaja Yoga,

265
00:31:54,615 --> 00:31:59,324
ngjiten shume lart, dhe papritur shkojne shume poshte.

266
00:32:00,407 --> 00:32:03,740
Me trishton shume, ekstremisht te trishtuar.

267
00:32:04,282 --> 00:32:07,532
Arsyeja eshte se ata nuk kane besim

268
00:32:07,906 --> 00:32:14,490
"besim tek vetja dhe besim ne Sahaj."

269
00:32:15,781 --> 00:32:18,574
Ky eshte besimi qe mungon.

270
00:32:19,157 --> 00:32:23,781
Ju duhet te keni besim tek vetja dhe besim tek Sahaj.

271
00:32:24,365 --> 00:32:28,740
Sahaj do te thote qe ka (gjendet) Fuqia hyjnore,

272
00:32:30,490 --> 00:32:37,073
dhe e gjithe kjo Fuqi perhapese kujdeset per ne.

273
00:32:39,990 --> 00:32:44,781
Edhe tani ndihet, ju e ndjete kete.

274
00:32:45,115 --> 00:32:46,906
Nuk eshte se vetem duke e thene ajo eshte aty

275
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:49,324
"e keni ditur qe eshte keshtu."

276
00:32:49,656 --> 00:32:51,324
Por vetem duke e ditur kete,

277
00:32:51,656 --> 00:32:55,157
nuk eshte bere besim brenda jush.

278
00:32:55,615 --> 00:32:59,407
Por ky eshte besimi per te cilin foli Krishti.

279
00:32:59,823 --> 00:33:02,282
Ky eshte besim me nje mendje te ndritur,

280
00:33:02,614 --> 00:33:04,115
jo besim i verber.

281
00:33:04,532 --> 00:33:07,948
Dhe me te verberin ju mund te beni gabime,

282
00:33:08,490 --> 00:33:12,490
ndersa me te ndriturin (ndricuarin) ju keni besim

283
00:33:12,781 --> 00:33:17,740
ju beheni ekstremisht te fuqishem, ekstremisht te fuqishem.

284
00:33:18,198 --> 00:33:20,365
Nuk mund te kete probleme

285
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:24,198
nese besimi juaj eshte i ndritur.

286
00:33:25,740 --> 00:33:27,865
Pra tani, ju shihni ne Sahaja Yoga

287
00:33:28,282 --> 00:33:31,698
shume njerez qe jane shume te qendrueshem,

288
00:33:33,614 --> 00:33:36,615
qe jane te drejte,

289
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:39,490
qe jane shume te vlefshem.

290
00:33:40,032 --> 00:33:41,823
Ata jane si njerezit

291
00:33:42,198 --> 00:33:45,365
qe e dine se po qendrojne ne shkembinj.

292
00:33:45,906 --> 00:33:49,948
Por ata te cilet nuk jane ende te qendrueshem jane njerezit,

293
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:53,365
qe mendojne se jane duke u tkurrur

294
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:59,449
ne disa lloj ujrash qesharake te kesaj jete.

295
00:34:01,574 --> 00:34:05,656
Shkembinjte kane qene aty, ju po qendroni mbi shkembinj;

296
00:34:06,115 --> 00:34:10,282
dhe kjo gjithashtu ka ardhur prej besimit

297
00:34:10,615 --> 00:34:13,781
se asgje s'mund te na shqetesoje, kete besim,

298
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:16,781
askush nuk na e trazon.

299
00:34:17,324 --> 00:34:20,615
Deri sa Krishti eshte i shqetesuar, natyrisht.

300
00:34:21,032 --> 00:34:22,698
E kam fjalen, Ai di gjithcka,

301
00:34:23,073 --> 00:34:25,115
pra Ai ishte i sigurte per kete.

302
00:34:25,614 --> 00:34:29,282
Ai kurre s'u merzit, Ai kurre nuk u tkurr, Ai kurre nuk dyshoi.

303
00:34:29,781 --> 00:34:33,324
E dinte qe, qe Ai ishte Djali i Zotit,

304
00:34:33,740 --> 00:34:36,365
dhe ky ishte nje fakt qe Ai e dinte mjaft mire.

305
00:34:36,781 --> 00:34:39,532
Dhe Ai kurre nuk e sfidoi kete, Ai kurre nuk e dyshoi, fare.

306
00:34:39,906 --> 00:34:41,781
Keshtu eshte.

307
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:46,449
Dhe prandaj Ai, them ishte duke qendruar mbi shkembinj;

308
00:34:46,906 --> 00:34:50,282
ndersa njerezit e tjere,

309
00:34:52,990 --> 00:34:54,906
edhe Sahaja yogis,

310
00:34:55,282 --> 00:34:58,574
duhet te behen si Krishti

311
00:34:58,906 --> 00:35:01,823
per aq sa ka te beje me besimin.

312
00:35:02,407 --> 00:35:06,781
Ky besim duhet te jete i kuptuar.

313
00:35:07,656 --> 00:35:10,407
Ky eshte nje besim i ndritur.

314
00:35:10,823 --> 00:35:15,115
Si Krishti "Ai shkoi ne kryqezim,

315
00:35:15,532 --> 00:35:17,990
Ai u fut ne gjithe llojet e gjerave,

316
00:35:18,449 --> 00:35:22,407
thjesht sepse Ai e dinte se ishte vetem nje drame (loje)

317
00:35:22,740 --> 00:35:27,032
dhe Ai ishte duke bere kete si nje loje  duke luajtur;"

318
00:35:27,490 --> 00:35:30,781
dhe nuk ka asgje serioze,

319
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:32,948
asgje nuk ka rendesi,
,

320
00:35:33,282 --> 00:35:34,781
dhe ia do te ringjalle Veten e Tij.

321
00:35:35,157 --> 00:35:37,407
Ai luajti pjesen.

322
00:35:37,906 --> 00:35:41,365
Per Ate nuk ishte fare serioze.

323
00:35:43,781 --> 00:35:47,614
Ai pa njerez ta vinin ne loje Ate, ta tallni Ate.

324
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:52,365
Ai gjithashtu ne zemren e Vet dinte gjithcka qe

325
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:56,740
"Keta njerez te cilet po me tallin nuk e dijne se kush jam."

326
00:35:57,449 --> 00:36:01,614
Por ne te njejten kohe,

327
00:36:02,615 --> 00:36:05,532
Ai ishte trupezimi i besimit:

328
00:36:06,032 --> 00:36:10,532
besim ne Veten e tij

329
00:36:10,865 --> 00:36:14,614
dhe ne kete Fuqi gjithe perhapese.

330
00:36:16,032 --> 00:36:18,324
Kjo asnjehere nuk ju mposht,

331
00:36:18,781 --> 00:36:23,698
por per kete ju duhet te keni besim absolut.

332
00:36:24,407 --> 00:36:29,157
Supozojme se kam dike tek i cili kam besim,

333
00:36:30,407 --> 00:36:34,490
natyrisht qe do i jap atij gjithe punen,

334
00:36:35,073 --> 00:36:37,407
Do i besoj gjithcka,

335
00:36:37,823 --> 00:36:40,740
Do i mbaj celsat me te ose parate me te.

336
00:36:41,073 --> 00:36:44,365
asnje dyshim ndaj nje personi te tille.

337
00:36:45,532 --> 00:36:50,781
Ne te njejten menyre nese ke besim "Besim ne veten tuaj,

338
00:36:51,449 --> 00:36:58,240
besim ne Sahaja Yoga kur jeni te stabilizuar"

339
00:36:59,032 --> 00:37:03,157
do te habiteni si do fillojne gjerat te funksionojne,

340
00:37:04,948 --> 00:37:06,740
si do te permiresohet jeta

341
00:37:07,198 --> 00:37:12,324
dhe do te qendroni ne kembe mbi shkembinj, keshtu do te ndiheni.

342
00:37:12,865 --> 00:37:15,157
Nuk do te keni dyshime,

343
00:37:15,532 --> 00:37:20,282
nuk do te keni probleme, semundje.

344
00:37:22,906 --> 00:37:27,073
Pra, kjo eshte nje lloj gjendjeje

345
00:37:27,614 --> 00:37:29,324
"vetem besim."

346
00:37:29,823 --> 00:37:32,574
Por tani kete besim, si e fitoni?

347
00:37:32,990 --> 00:37:37,157
Problemi eshte, si te fitoni (keni) kete besim?

348
00:37:37,532 --> 00:37:38,948
Nuk ka kurs per te,

349
00:37:39,365 --> 00:37:41,157
nuk ka literature per te,

350
00:37:41,532 --> 00:37:43,781
nuk ka leksione per te.

351
00:37:44,198 --> 00:37:49,656
Por ka nje zgjim brenda jush

352
00:37:50,115 --> 00:37:54,157
qe do jua kerkoje kete

353
00:37:54,740 --> 00:37:57,198
"Kush jam Une" ky zgjim,

354
00:37:57,574 --> 00:37:59,990
"Cfare jam Une? Cfare kam arritur?"

355
00:38:00,365 --> 00:38:05,823
Kuptoni, kete do pyesni

356
00:38:07,906 --> 00:38:11,698
"Cfare eshte ajo qe kam arritur?

357
00:38:12,115 --> 00:38:15,365
Cfare kam marre prej Sahaja Yoga?"

358
00:38:15,823 --> 00:38:18,407
Do ju vijne gjithe keto pyetje.

359
00:38:18,906 --> 00:38:20,948
Por nese ju keni besim,

360
00:38:21,407 --> 00:38:23,781
jo te verber por te ndritur

361
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:26,740
qe eshte formuar prej shume mrekullish ne jete,

362
00:38:27,115 --> 00:38:28,240
shume gjera ne jete;

363
00:38:28,614 --> 00:38:31,407
do kuptoni qe gjera te vogla,vogla kane qene mrekullira,

364
00:38:31,740 --> 00:38:32,948
gjera te vogla te vogla.

365
00:38:33,282 --> 00:38:35,365
Ka patur mrekullira edhe ne gjera te medha,

366
00:38:35,740 --> 00:38:39,490
ne kaq gjera qe nuk e keni pritur kurre te ndodhin.

367
00:38:39,906 --> 00:38:41,532
Pra tani e dini, e zgjidhur mjaft mire,

368
00:38:41,948 --> 00:38:45,449
qe ju jeni shume te mire ne Sahaja Yoga.

369
00:38:45,781 --> 00:38:48,532
Per shembull, filloi te bjere shi.

370
00:38:49,032 --> 00:38:52,115
Gjysma juaj mund te merzitet per kete, pse po bie shi,

371
00:38:52,532 --> 00:38:55,157
por ata do e dijne qe gjendet nje cati shume e bukur,

372
00:38:55,532 --> 00:38:56,740
s'mund te ndodhe asgje.

373
00:38:57,115 --> 00:38:59,282
Le te bjere shi sa te doje.

374
00:38:59,656 --> 00:39:03,407
Dhe atehere do te keni besimin qe nuk do te bjere shi,

375
00:39:03,823 --> 00:39:05,490
nuk do te na beje qulle (lage).

376
00:39:05,823 --> 00:39:10,990
Ne te njejten menyre ky besim brenda nesh

377
00:39:11,365 --> 00:39:15,073
duhet te jete absolutisht solid,

378
00:39:15,823 --> 00:39:19,740
dhe kjo ju ben ekstremisht te forte

379
00:39:20,198 --> 00:39:22,615
dhe ju ben pergjegjes

380
00:39:22,990 --> 00:39:25,240
per ringjalljen e mijerave

381
00:39:25,574 --> 00:39:30,032
dhe mijera e mijera e mijera njerezve.

382
00:39:35,449 --> 00:39:39,449
Kjo lloj jete qe kemi

383
00:39:40,865 --> 00:39:46,532
"qe vetem nga stabilizimi (formimi) yne,

384
00:39:46,990 --> 00:39:50,615
nga mirekuptimi yne,

385
00:39:51,073 --> 00:39:56,656
nga vezhgimi yne qe kemi vendosur brenda vetes sone,

386
00:39:57,698 --> 00:40:00,240
ne qendrojme ne Sahaja Yoga

387
00:40:01,449 --> 00:40:04,823
"eshte dicka e mrekullueshme, por do duhej, duhet te ndodhe,

388
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:09,407
po ndodh, dhe duhet t'u ndodhe te gjithe juve.

389
00:40:09,906 --> 00:40:14,032
Te gjithe duhet te keni fatin

390
00:40:14,614 --> 00:40:18,198
te njihni shpirtin tuaj

391
00:40:18,656 --> 00:40:22,823
dhe te njihni veten.

392
00:40:23,614 --> 00:40:26,282
Pra njeriu duhet te kete besim tek vetja.

393
00:40:26,740 --> 00:40:28,948
Shoh qe disa Sahaja yoginis vijne gjithmone e thone,

394
00:40:29,365 --> 00:40:32,324
"Nene, nuk jam mire, Jam e padobishme, nuk po punoj.

395
00:40:32,656 --> 00:40:36,698
"Une jam nje kokerr dembele," apo cfaredo qofte.

396
00:40:39,948 --> 00:40:43,781
Ne rregull, ju e mendoni keshtu "kerkoni" per te.

397
00:40:44,656 --> 00:40:47,407
Cfare doni?

398
00:40:47,823 --> 00:40:52,073
Edhe nese nuk kerkoni do te funksionoje,

399
00:40:54,032 --> 00:40:56,032
edhe nese nuk kerkoni.

400
00:40:56,490 --> 00:41:01,990
Edhe sikur vetem te mendoni per te, do te funksionoje.

401
00:41:02,574 --> 00:41:05,906
Edhe nese do i kushtoni vemendje do te funksionoje,

402
00:41:06,407 --> 00:41:08,948
sepse kjo Fuqi gjithe-perhapese

403
00:41:09,490 --> 00:41:11,073
eshte e vetmja fuqi e vertete.

404
00:41:11,449 --> 00:41:14,365
gjithe pjesa tjeter e fuqive eshte e padobishme.

405
00:41:15,198 --> 00:41:21,948
Dhe eshte kaq efikase, kaq e dhembshur

406
00:41:22,615 --> 00:41:29,698
qe ne ndarjen e sekondes mund te rregulloje gjerat.

407
00:41:31,073 --> 00:41:34,365
Dje patem dike nga Australia,

408
00:41:34,781 --> 00:41:36,449
dhe ishte mashtruar nga dikush

409
00:41:36,865 --> 00:41:39,282
duke blere nje toke dhe nje shtepi

410
00:41:39,698 --> 00:41:43,614
me nje cmim shume te tepruar, per te cilen ai nuk kishte para.

411
00:41:44,073 --> 00:41:44,990
Dhe ky shoku tha,

412
00:41:45,282 --> 00:41:46,823
"Nuk ka rendesi edhe sikur te mos kesh para,

413
00:41:47,198 --> 00:41:48,906
s'ka problem."

414
00:41:49,240 --> 00:41:51,614
Ai i besoi atij "pati besim te gabuar",

415
00:41:51,906 --> 00:41:55,615
Mund te them, dhe me pas tha, "Ne rregull."

416
00:41:55,948 --> 00:42:01,490
Ai pagoi gjithe parate qe kishte, vetem per ta rezervuar.

417
00:42:03,614 --> 00:42:08,449
Dikush shkoi atje, ishte nje puja keshtu qe shkuan shume atje.

418
00:42:11,240 --> 00:42:14,948
Kaq shume puja, dhe ndodhen gjera,

419
00:42:15,365 --> 00:42:18,282
dhe erdhen kaq shume njerez te shihnin gjithe kete.

420
00:42:18,698 --> 00:42:22,823
Por ky shoku ishte kaq i shqetesuar, shume i shqetesuar,

421
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:24,490
nuk mund ta kuptonte,

422
00:42:24,906 --> 00:42:26,490
"Pse me ndodhi mua

423
00:42:26,906 --> 00:42:30,865
qe te vihem ne nje situate te tille te veshtire?"

424
00:42:32,656 --> 00:42:34,532
Ai ishte mashtruar dhe ishte,

425
00:42:35,198 --> 00:42:37,532
e kam fjalen, absolutisht i befasuar.

426
00:42:37,948 --> 00:42:41,698
Ai nuk e kish idene se si mund te dilte nga kjo rremuje.

427
00:42:42,240 --> 00:42:45,532
Ai kish futur aty te gjitha parate, ishte perfshire me gjithcka,

428
00:42:45,906 --> 00:42:52,115
dhe nese nuk do i paguante parate mund te futej ne burg.

429
00:42:53,865 --> 00:42:58,157
Une thjesht i shkrova "Ki besim tek vetja."

430
00:42:58,574 --> 00:43:01,656
Kjo eshte e gjitha "Ki besim."

431
00:43:02,282 --> 00:43:04,365
Dhe cfare mrekullie ndodhi,

432
00:43:04,740 --> 00:43:09,490
qe dikush tjeter ofroi per te nje cmim shume me te larte.

433
00:43:12,614 --> 00:43:14,449
Dhe shoku i kish thene,

434
00:43:14,906 --> 00:43:17,865
"Sigurisht une do te paguaj cfaredo qe te kam premtuar.

435
00:43:18,324 --> 00:43:21,282
Do te kthej parate, dhe me shume

436
00:43:21,698 --> 00:43:25,532
se me duhet te paguaja."

