536
00:49:14,865 --> 00:49:17,615
shumica e njererzve nuk do te jene me.

537
00:49:18,073 --> 00:49:19,532
Jo se ne s'jemi te gatshem,

538
00:49:19,948 --> 00:49:25,614
por sepse ata nuk jane te destinuar

539
00:49:26,198 --> 00:49:27,865
te vijne ne Sahaja Yoga,

540
00:49:28,198 --> 00:49:30,490
s'eshte e thene te vijne ne Sahaja Yoga.

541
00:49:30,865 --> 00:49:32,407
Pra, ju jeni kaq fatlume

542
00:49:32,781 --> 00:49:36,656
qe keni arritur realizimin tuaj, rilindjen tuaj.

543
00:49:37,032 --> 00:49:40,032
