563
00:50:52,282 --> 00:50:56,615
"Sepse si mund te kete kaq shume mjerim ne kete bote?

564
00:50:57,032 --> 00:50:58,990
Si mund te kete nje femije te verber,

565
00:50:59,282 --> 00:51:01,781
