567
00:51:04,990 --> 00:51:06,823
I them, "Me ke treguar gjithcka?"
"Po".

568
00:51:07,240 --> 00:51:10,532
I them, "Tani, supozojme te themi qe

569
00:51:10,781 --> 00:51:15,823
