591
00:52:38,656 --> 00:52:41,490
E dini dikush kishte xhaxhain semure,

592
00:52:41,865 --> 00:52:43,115
e nuk ishte nje Sahaja Yogi.

593
00:52:43,614 --> 00:52:47,240
Ai shkoi ta vizitonte ate, dhe gruaja e tij i thote qe

594
00:52:47,614 --> 00:52:49,865
"Ti je i afte t'i lutesh Nenes.

595
00:52:50,365 --> 00:52:54,781
Pse nuk i thua Asaj te me beje mire burrin?"

596
00:52:55,198 --> 00:52:57,990
Ai ishte nje i semure me kancer ne shtratin e vdekjes.

597
00:52:58,449 --> 00:53:01,198
Ai tha, "Ne rregull." Ai vetem u perul dhe u lut,

598
00:53:01,532 --> 00:53:03,698
"Nene, te lutem sheroje xhaxhain tim."

599
00:53:04,115 --> 00:53:05,574
