640
00:55:31,449 --> 00:55:34,324
Asgje nuk ju lidh,

641
00:55:34,781 --> 00:55:36,532
asgje nuk ju shemb,

642
00:55:36,865 --> 00:55:40,698
asnje zakon nuk ju kthehet;

643
00:55:42,698 --> 00:55:47,990
sepse besimi do ju pastroje teresisht,

644
00:55:48,574 --> 00:55:51,615
